and enlightened me♪

4
00:00:26,421 --> 00:00:32,996
♪I crossed the sea of suffering
but couldn't escape your gaze♪

5
00:00:33,192 --> 00:00:39,930
♪Look at the bright moon
across the Milky Way♪

6
00:00:40,060 --> 00:00:46,996
♪All love poems will record our story
from now on♪

7
00:00:47,061 --> 00:00:53,700
♪The thought of the distant mountain
makes my heart ache for my hometown♪

8
00:00:53,840 --> 00:01:01,520
♪Stone of Three Lifetimes reflects fate.
You once rode past on horseback♪

9
00:01:02,020 --> 00:01:03,480
=Just Wanna Be With You=

10
00:01:03,480 --> 00:01:05,367
(Adapted
From Zhihu Novelist, Little Qi's)

11
00:01:05,367 --> 00:01:07,260
("Three Marriages
to the Underworld Lord")

12
00:01:07,260 --> 00:01:10,260
=Episode 1=

13
00:01:16,560 --> 00:01:18,239
Heavenly Gate opened.

14
00:01:18,599 --> 00:01:20,159
All clans came to celebrate.

15
00:01:20,640 --> 00:01:23,159
The champion of Cangyun's
centennial gladiatorial competition

16
00:01:23,719 --> 00:01:26,920
will enjoy eternal immortality.

17
00:02:02,160 --> 00:02:03,120
Why aren't you watching?

18
00:02:03,520 --> 00:02:05,200
Don't you think
it's cruel to enjoy watching

19
00:02:05,640 --> 00:02:06,879
different clans kill each other?

20
00:02:07,280 --> 00:02:09,159
They're all lowly beings.

21
00:02:09,840 --> 00:02:11,439
How is it cruel?

22
00:02:11,879 --> 00:02:14,919
Cangyun's gladiatorial ceremony
is held once every century.

23
00:02:15,159 --> 00:02:16,800
Just being noticed by us

24
00:02:16,840 --> 00:02:18,759
is already the highest honor
they could have.

25
00:02:18,840 --> 00:02:19,599
But...

26
00:02:20,479 --> 00:02:21,199
Yu.

27
00:02:39,000 --> 00:02:39,759
(Jiu.)

28
00:02:40,240 --> 00:02:40,919
(Yu.)

29
00:02:41,599 --> 00:02:43,199
(I finally got to see you again.)

30
00:02:45,680 --> 00:02:47,240
(Everyone says celestial clan is noble,)

31
00:02:47,560 --> 00:02:49,719
(but I've never seen
such a real wilderness.)

32
00:02:50,800 --> 00:02:52,400
(Thank you, Jiu.)

33
00:02:53,360 --> 00:02:54,800
I want to give you this freedom.

34
00:02:55,159 --> 00:02:55,919
Do you like it?

35
00:02:57,080 --> 00:02:57,919
Yes.

36
00:03:02,639 --> 00:03:05,319
(May your heart mirror mine.)

37
00:03:06,280 --> 00:03:09,199
(I will never let you down.)

38
00:03:10,960 --> 00:03:13,919
Lingxiao clan and Cangyun
have been married for generations.

39
00:03:14,159 --> 00:03:15,360
You don't even know that?

40
00:03:16,120 --> 00:03:17,039
You only told me

41
00:03:17,040 --> 00:03:18,840
to come to Cangyun
to learn summoning technique

42
00:03:18,960 --> 00:03:20,080
and awaken the spirit stone.

43
00:03:20,360 --> 00:03:22,080
You never told me about marriage.

44
00:03:22,240 --> 00:03:25,080
Soon you will become
the mistress of Cangyun.

45
00:03:25,199 --> 00:03:26,360
If you refuse to marry,

46
00:03:27,000 --> 00:03:29,960
the entire Lingxiao clan
will be destroyed.

47
00:03:32,159 --> 00:03:34,159
Marriage between Lingxiao and Cangyun

48
00:03:34,360 --> 00:03:35,719
is a thousand-year-old tradition.

49
00:03:36,039 --> 00:03:37,000
If I refuse to marry,

50
00:03:37,280 --> 00:03:39,120
our entire clan will be destroyed.

51
00:03:39,240 --> 00:03:40,000
I'm sorry.

52
00:03:40,120 --> 00:03:41,560
Let's stop seeing each other.

53
00:03:43,800 --> 00:03:44,479
(Yu.)

54
00:03:45,319 --> 00:03:47,719
(I learned forbidden techniques
and broke into Cangyun)

55
00:03:48,879 --> 00:03:50,039
(just to see you again.)

56
00:03:51,520 --> 00:03:52,400
(I'm here.)

57
00:03:53,960 --> 00:03:56,680
(Jiu, you shouldn't have come.)

58
00:03:56,800 --> 00:03:58,000
What's your name?

59
00:03:58,319 --> 00:03:59,000
Jiu.

60
00:03:59,439 --> 00:04:00,800
I'm in good mood today,

61
00:04:01,160 --> 00:04:02,560
so I will accept you as my disciple.

62
00:04:03,719 --> 00:04:04,960
What reward do you want?

63
00:04:06,560 --> 00:04:07,319
I want her.

64
00:04:17,000 --> 00:04:19,000
How dare you speak nonsense?

65
00:04:26,800 --> 00:04:28,040
What a bold foxfolk slave.

66
00:04:28,519 --> 00:04:30,720
How dare you go after Goddess?

67
00:04:39,040 --> 00:04:39,720
Your Excellency.

68
00:04:39,760 --> 00:04:42,070
We foxfolk have been subservient
to Cangyun for generations.

69
00:04:42,079 --> 00:04:44,319
Please consider the peace of our clans

70
00:04:45,199 --> 00:04:46,480
and spare him.

71
00:04:46,800 --> 00:04:48,399
You're the same.

72
00:04:54,560 --> 00:04:55,399
Good disciple.

73
00:04:56,279 --> 00:04:57,680
After entering Cangyun,

74
00:04:58,680 --> 00:05:00,759
you must submit to me forever.

75
00:05:01,759 --> 00:05:02,439
Otherwise...

76
00:05:10,079 --> 00:05:10,839
Your Excellency.

77
00:05:13,519 --> 00:05:15,639
You and I will be married soon.

78
00:05:16,160 --> 00:05:18,399
Taking a new disciple
is a double blessing.

79
00:05:19,920 --> 00:05:20,680
Spare him.

80
00:05:32,720 --> 00:05:33,560
Alright!

81
00:05:36,519 --> 00:05:37,720
Double blessing.

82
00:05:38,160 --> 00:05:39,879
Cangyun's blessings are endless.

83
00:05:40,079 --> 00:05:41,959
