87
00:05:48,920 --> 00:05:51,079
Sovereign is blessed with longevity.

88
00:05:51,660 --> 00:05:54,020
(Cangyun)

89
00:05:57,199 --> 00:05:59,600
You exchanged glances
with that foxfolk today.

90
00:05:59,720 --> 00:06:01,040
Do you have any ulterior motives?

91
00:06:03,839 --> 00:06:05,000
For thousands of years,

92
00:06:05,279 --> 00:06:07,680
Lingxiao married Cangyun clan

93
00:06:07,759 --> 00:06:09,120
to receive protection.

94
00:06:11,800 --> 00:06:13,360
Don't let me catch you.

95
00:06:31,399 --> 00:06:31,959
Jiu!

96
00:06:32,519 --> 00:06:34,199
Why risk joining a duel?

97
00:06:34,480 --> 00:06:37,199
Only by entering Cangyun
can we get the spirit stone

98
00:06:38,480 --> 00:06:40,439
and protect foxfolk.

99
00:06:40,639 --> 00:06:41,720
You and I have meager magic.

100
00:06:41,879 --> 00:06:43,120
We can't rival Nangong Xiao.

101
00:06:43,519 --> 00:06:44,360
I entered Cangyun

102
00:06:45,079 --> 00:06:46,360
also because I wanted to see her.

103
00:06:46,800 --> 00:06:47,600
I advise you

104
00:06:48,199 --> 00:06:50,000
not to have ideas
about Sovereign's woman.

105
00:06:50,600 --> 00:06:52,040
You and I are humble to the bone.

106
00:06:52,879 --> 00:06:53,920
Only by surrendering

107
00:06:54,399 --> 00:06:56,439
can we preserve the peace of our clans.

108
00:07:00,400 --> 00:07:01,279
Take care of yourself.

109
00:07:03,199 --> 00:07:04,839
(I know she was forced.)

110
00:07:05,399 --> 00:07:06,439
(I want to take her away.)

111
00:07:07,000 --> 00:07:08,199
(I don't want to give up.)

112
00:07:08,661 --> 00:07:11,020
(Cangyun)

113
00:07:21,959 --> 00:07:24,040
You've worked hard
for the glory of the two clans.

114
00:07:25,879 --> 00:07:27,079
You must serve as my eyes.

115
00:07:27,240 --> 00:07:28,639
Awakening the ancient spirit stone

116
00:07:28,879 --> 00:07:30,319
is the duty of all Goddesses.

117
00:07:30,720 --> 00:07:32,959
It's my duty
to take care of the Goddess.

118
00:07:33,480 --> 00:07:36,240
Have you found
the entrance to demon clan's forest?

119
00:07:36,680 --> 00:07:37,920
Rest assured, Your Excellency.

120
00:07:37,959 --> 00:07:39,600
I've sent people to search for it.

121
00:07:41,240 --> 00:07:43,120
Once I find demon clan's spirit stone,

122
00:07:43,600 --> 00:07:44,879
unifying the three realms

123
00:07:46,480 --> 00:07:47,879
is just around the corner.

