127
00:08:04,480 --> 00:08:05,319
Jiu?

128
00:08:09,279 --> 00:08:10,160
Why are you here?

129
00:08:10,520 --> 00:08:11,959
I'm here to take you away from here.

130
00:08:15,560 --> 00:08:16,959
I can't leave Cangyun.

131
00:08:17,360 --> 00:08:18,240
My clan

132
00:08:19,160 --> 00:08:20,680
still needs Cangyun's protection.

133
00:08:21,759 --> 00:08:22,480
Yu.

134
00:08:23,000 --> 00:08:24,680
He just treats you as a tool.

135
00:08:24,959 --> 00:08:26,720
He wants you to help him
summon spirit stones.

136
00:08:26,839 --> 00:08:27,680
Don't you get it yet?

137
00:08:31,000 --> 00:08:31,759
Nangong Xiao

138
00:08:32,200 --> 00:08:34,159
commits all evil
in the guise of a celestial being.

139
00:08:34,320 --> 00:08:35,559
He won't spare you.

140
00:08:41,120 --> 00:08:43,759
I'll find a way
to protect you and your clan.

141
00:08:43,879 --> 00:08:44,600
Believe me.

142
00:08:45,799 --> 00:08:46,679
But...

143
00:08:46,879 --> 00:08:47,720
Come with me.

144
00:08:49,279 --> 00:08:49,840
Hurry up.

145
00:08:55,279 --> 00:08:55,879
(Jiu.)

146
00:08:56,799 --> 00:08:58,679
(Why don't you listen to advice?)

147
00:09:03,399 --> 00:09:04,000
Yu.

148
00:09:10,200 --> 00:09:10,840
(Yu.)

149
00:09:11,279 --> 00:09:12,759
(Nangong Xiao won't spare you.)

150
00:09:17,720 --> 00:09:18,919
(Oh no, what should I do?)

151
00:09:28,279 --> 00:09:29,720
Greetings, Saintess.

152
00:09:30,080 --> 00:09:32,159
How's your cultivation progressing?

153
00:09:32,679 --> 00:09:34,399
It has always been smooth.

154
00:09:37,200 --> 00:09:39,320
If there's nothing else, please go back.

155
00:09:42,679 --> 00:09:43,399
Where's Luo Ying?

156
00:09:46,200 --> 00:09:47,000
She...

157
00:09:50,120 --> 00:09:52,720
She went to the forest
to collect divine dew for me.

158
00:09:54,159 --> 00:09:56,039
You two are usually inseparable,

159
00:09:57,080 --> 00:09:59,080
but I didn't see her today.

160
00:10:08,276 --> 00:10:14,094
♪Dark clouds cover the stars
without a trace of light♪

161
00:10:15,607 --> 00:10:20,087
♪Waiting for the wind
to clear the grey away♪

162
00:10:22,341 --> 00:10:25,912
♪Sudden rain falls
and I get soaked alone♪

163
00:10:26,007 --> 00:10:29,716
♪Even larks know where they belong♪

164
00:10:30,058 --> 00:10:35,534
♪It is not about running away♪

165
00:10:37,374 --> 00:10:43,730
♪I search for you across the vast sky,
but where are you now?♪

166
00:10:44,603 --> 00:10:49,687
♪I become a wisp of wind,
wiping away the clouds' traces♪

167
00:10:51,534 --> 00:10:54,974
♪I long to disappear without a trace,
wrapped in mystery♪

168
00:10:55,083 --> 00:10:58,756
♪If I send your loneliness
back to the sky♪

169
00:10:59,149 --> 00:11:04,509
♪It can only rest inside your dreams♪

170
00:11:04,625 --> 00:11:09,600
♪You and I gaze
at the endless Milky Way♪

171
00:11:09,600 --> 00:11:11,738
♪Holding each other so near♪

172
00:11:11,963 --> 00:11:19,112
♪If I were granted
a pair of splendid wings♪

173
00:11:19,178 --> 00:11:24,189
♪I could chase memories
in place of the right to love♪

174
00:11:24,240 --> 00:11:26,836
♪But the Milky Way never ends♪

175
00:11:26,923 --> 00:11:33,636
♪In this thin robe,
I wait for your reply♪
